# ğŸ“¤ Telegram Copier Bot

A Python bot that automatically copies and forwards messages (including media) from one Telegram chat/channel/group to another using [Telethon](https://github.com/LonamiWebs/Telethon).

## ğŸ“Œ What This Bot Can Do

âœ… Copy all messages from any source chat to a target chat  
âœ… Supports text, images, videos, files, and more  
âœ… Filter messages by type or keyword  
âœ… Works with groups, channels, or private chats  
âœ… Secure session login with reusability

